  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      15 patients with narcolepsy and 15 healthy controls will be included in the study. According
      to a randomized, double-blind protocol they will receive intranasally at night first Orexine
      A and approximately two weeks later placebo or vice versa. Thereafter sleep will be recorded,
      the cytokine-system and neurocognition characterized.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
